---
title: "Figure 5.7: Sequence Diagram — Admin Scholarship Management"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant AB as AdminBrowser
    participant PH as PortalRequestHandler
    participant DB as Database

    AB->>PH: GET /admin/login
    PH-->>AB: Render admin_login.html

    AB->>PH: POST /admin/login (username, password)
    PH->>PH: Verify admin credentials
    PH-->>AB: Set admin session cookie, Redirect to /admin

    AB->>PH: GET /admin
    PH->>DB: SELECT * FROM scholarships
    DB-->>PH: All scholarship records
    PH-->>AB: Render admin.html (dashboard with scholarship list)

    AB->>PH: POST /admin/add_scholarship (name, provider, description, eligibility_criteria, deadline, link)
    PH->>DB: INSERT INTO scholarships (name, provider, description, eligibility_criteria, deadline, link)
    DB-->>PH: OK
    PH-->>AB: Redirect to /admin?msg=added

    AB->>PH: GET /admin/edit_scholarship?id=5
    PH->>DB: SELECT * FROM scholarships WHERE id = 5
    DB-->>PH: Scholarship record
    PH-->>AB: Render edit_scholarship.html (pre-filled form)

    AB->>PH: POST /admin/edit_scholarship (id=5, updated fields)
    PH->>DB: UPDATE scholarships SET ... WHERE id = 5
    DB-->>PH: OK
    PH-->>AB: Redirect to /admin?msg=updated

    AB->>PH: POST /admin/delete_scholarship (id=5)
    PH->>DB: DELETE FROM scholarships WHERE id = 5
    DB-->>PH: OK
    PH-->>AB: Redirect to /admin?msg=deleted
